---
// No props needed
---

<section class="resume-section scroll-reveal-animate">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  
  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"
        ><strong>Philadelphia Pointing Span Test</strong></span
      >
      <span class="date">4 months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Created a web application consisting of a neuropsychological test for
        patients to help identify signs of neurodegenerative illness
      </li>
      <li>
        Key contributions (7-person team):
        <ul>
          <li>
            Architected and implemented the core backend system of the user API
          </li>
          <li>
            Created a web application for the doctor to view, compare, and
            analyze data with visuals and statistics</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"><strong>KFT Grocery Store Database</strong></span>
      <span class="date">4 Months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Developed a SQL database to for a grocery store
      </li>
      <li>
        Created presentation and graphs to highlight the purpose of the
        project
      </li>
      <li>
        Functionality includes monitoring products, creating reports for
        products and employees
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-entry">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="institution"><strong>Cased-Based Simulation</strong></span>
      <span class="date">4 Months</span>
    </div>
    <ul class="details">
      <li>
        Created an application for developers/users to create and take
        decision based simulations
      </li>
      <li>
        Developed a noSQL database to store simulations and
        developer/user information
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>


  <p class="more-projects-link">
    For more projects, check the <a href="/projects">Projects page</a>.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .resume-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  .project-entry {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem; /* Space between entries */
  }
  .project-entry:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .project-entry .header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .project-entry .date {
    font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .project-entry .details {
    list-style: disc; /* Use bullet points */
    padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Standard padding for list */
    margin-left: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .project-entry .details li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .project-entry .header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .project-entry .date {
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }
  }

  .more-projects-link {
    margin-top: 3rem; /* Add space above this line */
    font-size: 1.2 rem;
  }
</style>
